1 06:50:09 UTC","locale":null,"is_default":0},{"id":33,"title":"NRC Data Management Plan template Draft","description":"<p>The planning phases of NRC research projects must incorporate the development of a data management plan (DMP), which outlines the research/science data that will be generated or collected over the course of the project, relevant metadata, storage environment, security considerations, and plans for data archiving/disposition upon project completion.&nbsp; The&nbsp;DMP Template for the National Research Council Canada (NRC) is a streamlined, effective online tool for data planning. Consult the Guidelines to creating a Data Management plan (DMP, available on MyZone.</p>","published":1,"user_id":null,"organisation_id":39,"created_at":"2018-02-23 16:22:10 UTC","updated_at":"2018-03-15 14:32:05 UTC","locale":null,"is_default":null},{"id":35,"title":"University of Manitoba ","description":"<p>This&nbsp;template is designed for UM researchers with guidance links, when applicable and available,&nbsp;to specific resources and supports located or affiliated with the University of Manitoba.</p>","published":1,"user_id":null,"organisation_id":37,"created_at":"2018-02-23 21:55:36 UTC","updated_at":"2018-03-02 01:54:51 UTC","locale":null,"is_default":null},{"id":36,"title":"University of Manitoba Template B","description":"<p>This is the 2nd template for the University of Manitoba.&nbsp;</p>","published":null,"user_id":null,"organisation_id":37,"created_at":"2018-03-02 01:06:46 UTC","updated_at":"2018-03-02 01:06:46 UTC","locale":null,"is_default":null},{"id":37,"title":"Test OMAFRA-UG DMP template","description":"<p>Test OMAFRA-UG questions for DMP OMAFRA template</p>","published":null,"user_id":null,"organisation_id":22,"created_at":"2018-06-11 14:29:04 UTC","updated_at":"2018-06-12 14:18:48 UTC","locale":null,"is_default":null},{"id":43,"title":"Université de Montréal","description":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Université de Montréal</span></p>","p